  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 04/11/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.4-Enhancements\">Enhancements</h3><ul><li><p>Improved currency support for Square users outside of the US.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.4-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Resolved the Error 500 experienced when closing out a VCT with Square enabled.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an error which had been preventing users with Bluefin and Heartland devices from being able to perform test transactions.</p></li><li><p>The &quot;Download Location Overrides with Defaults&quot; button, which had stopped functioning, now works as expected again.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an error where text boxes were not displaying in Custom Forms in certain scenarios.</p></li></ul>",
